Package: libhttp-message-perl
Description-md5: d0d09bc69619d7907570bf158f4d4197
Description-hr: perl sučelje za poruke HTTP izgleda
 The HTTP::Message distribution contains classes useful for representing
 the messages passed in HTTP style communication. These are classes
 representing requests, responses and the headers contained within them.
 .
 The HTTP::Headers class encapsulates HTTP-style message headers. The
 headers consist of attribute-value pairs also called fields, which may be
 repeated, and which are printed in a particular order. The field names are
 cases insensitive.
 .
 Instances of this class are usually created as member variables of the
 HTTP::Request and HTTP::Response classes, internal to the library.

Package: libhunspell-1.7-0
Description-md5: cd5cd2fd85fe0d5a33a798cf7034cf92
Description-hr: provjera pravopisa i morfološka analiza
 Hunspell služi za provjeru pravopisa i morfološku analizu biblioteka i
 programa dizajniran je za jezike s bogatom morfologijom i složenim
 sastavljanjem riječi ili kôdiranjem znakova. Temeljen je na MySpellu
 karakterizira ga Ispell terminalno sučelje koje koristi Curses biblioteku,
 Ispell sučelje i OpenOffice UNO modul.
 .
