Package: printer-driver-hpcups
Description-md5: ada0514587fab5c2bab3c115ac6c4800
Description-hr: HP Linux sustav za ispis i obradu slika - CUPS Raster upravljački program (hpcups)
 This package contains a CUPS-Raster-based printer driver which adds
 support for most inkjet printers and some LaserJet printers manufactured
 by HP. It does not provide PPDs for the fax functionality of HP's multi-
 function devices.
 .
 Korisnicima CUPS sustava za ispis se savjetuje da isto instaliraju hplip
 paket i koriste hp CUPS pozadinski program za slanje podataka u pisač.
 HPLIP podržava USB i mrežne uređaje i omogućuje proširenu hpcups
 funkcionalnost poput ispisa manjih rubova. Odabirom bilo koje hpcups ppd
 datoteke u CUPS će koristiti hpcups automatski.
 .
 No physical PPDs are shipped with this driver. PPDs are dynamically
 generated via a CUPS DDK .drv file.
 .
 This package can be installed to provide a minimal headless printer
 solution using CUPS.

Package: printer-driver-hpijs
Description-md5: 6ab962d256c4da1e18d9397ae22fbd86
Description-hr: HP Linux sustav za ispis i obradu slika - upravljački program za pisač (hpijs)
